title: Episode 136: To The Left (Feat. Neyo & Jasmine Brand)
itunes:title: Episode 136: To The Left (Feat. Neyo & Jasmine Brand)
description:
On this weeks episode, Neyo comes through to chat with the ladies of Lip Service and shares his evolution of becoming a "Good Man.' Neyo opens up about his savage life in the past, as well as the times he's had to say no in the bedroom. Also a major thank you to Jasmine Brand for joining us as a guest host!
